window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The complete four-book Legacy Series. Perfect for listeners who love urban fantasy filled with dangerous magic, deadly secrets, and slow-burn romantic tension.</b></p> <p><i>I survived by staying hidden. But secrets never stay buried.</i></p> <p>I’m Levy Michaels—an antique dealer by trade, fugitive by bloodline. When supernaturals were revealed to the world, they got PR teams, businesses, and their own guilds. If I wanted to live, I got the chance to stay hidden.</p> <p>Legacy-born, I’m heir to a kind of magic the world outlawed long ago. I’ve spent my life pretending to be human—and doing a damn good job of it. Until the day I don’t.</p> <p>An enchanted dagger vanishes from my shop. I wake up beside three dead supernaturals and no memory of what happened. Now I’m under investigation by Gareth Reynolds, the magnetic, calculating leader of the Supernatural Guild. He’s powerful, dangerous, and exactly the kind of man who could destroy me… if he doesn’t unravel me first.</p> <p>The good news? He doesn’t think I’m guilty.</p> <p>The bad news? He suspects I’m hiding something—and he’s not wrong.</p> <p>Clearing my name means trusting him. Surviving means keeping my secret. But in a world built on blood, power, and betrayal, there’s no hiding forever. And if the truth comes out, Gareth can’t save me. He may be the one who has to end me.</p> <p><b>The Legacy Series Boxed Set Includes:</b></p> <p><i>Double-Sided Magic<br> Obsidian Magic<br> Renegade Magic<br> Rogue Magic</i></p>"; 
